        Initial CLI: Examining "Leer:l3.0": OK
        Initial CLI: Unlocking "Leer:L3.0"
        Initial CLI: Loading segmented image "l3.0": OK
        Initial CLI: Getting shared lock (-2) on "l3.0": OK
        Initial CLI: Getting parent of "Leer:L3.0".
        Initial CLI: Unlocking "Leer:L3.0"
        Initial CLI: Changing current directory to "Leer:".


