         and contains the following stuff:

         1.At the start of the programm the adresss $66666 will be in-
         creased by 1.It  depends on the value  in  this  adress, what
         happens.A work of a beginnner ( I think ) because the  string
         "dos.library" can be found 4 times in this short file.
